    "Kose and Koc (2015) also emphasized AI's capacity to augment distance education, particularly when combined with other intelligent systems.",
    "Significant scope for research and exploration exists within this topic.",
    "Our paper prioritizes a comprehensive analysis encompassing both quantitative and qualitative aspects.",
    "It aims to explore various dimensions, such as the objectives of AI, its applications, and public awareness, and undertake a comparative evaluation of AI's role in education compared to traditional methodologies.",
